xnoremap k gk

nnoremap Q <Cmd>copen<CR>

" easy force write/quit
cnoreabbrev qq quit!
cnoreabbrev ww update!
cnoreabbrev w update

" easy open memo buffer
command! Scratch new +set\ buftype=nofile\ filetype=markdown
cnoreabbrev memo Scratch

" TODO
