" type "&" is too hard to me on JIS keyboard

" dont use clipboard
nnoremap x "_x
nnoremap s "_s
nnoremap c "_c

"" DONT USE ARROW TO MOVE
noremap <Left> <nop>
noremap <Down> <nop>
noremap <Up> <nop>
noremap <Right> <nop>
noremap! <Left> <nop>
noremap! <Down> <nop>
